message.body: Thanks again for the food today. Chris and I polished it off.
Oh, nice. I wound up polishing off a bottle of wine... hung out at Beau for a while and got good n drunk. Yeesh! Hope you're havin fun at the hotel party!
Yeah, you and me both. Sittin in front of the big TV watching Law and Order. Jelly brain. Maybe see you tomorrow.
I might swing by the gallery.
Cool. I work till 4. I'll check in later and see where you're at. Have a good night.
Want some taters and avo salsa?
One day you'll be sick of 'em. I'm almost there myself. You at the gallery?
